{"tid":2386196,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"馬斯克撐散戶：沽空根本是詐騙","createTime":"2021-01-29T12:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T12:55:05.000Z","uid":71215,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1baa5742700fae6aa350003f73bedfe0488ede28","tid":2386196,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:20:48.000Z","msg":"美股市場正上演一場「教材級案例、電影級素材」事件，討論區散戶合力炒高GameStop（美股代號：GME），試圖「夾淡倉」擊退沽空機構一事，引起白宮關注之餘，更逼到券商出動「只許平倉，不許建倉」的手段，禁止散戶買GME，以「控制風險」，做法令全球投資者嘩然。<br />\n.<br />\n一向不喜歡沽空機構的Tesla（美股代號：TSLA）行政總裁馬斯克疑似對事件看不過眼，在Twitter發文，指「你不能賣你沒有真正擁有的房屋或汽車；但你*可以*賣你沒有真正擁有的股票？這完全是亂來 &mdash;&mdash; 沽空根本是詐騙。」<br />\n.<br />\n事實上，Tesla一直是沽空機構的搵食對象（可惜失敗），單計2020年，Tesla股價累升7倍﹐據金融數據公司S3 Partners分析，2020年Tesla淡倉投資者損失金額逾400億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/142880139_1928896283932955_5605947646482050194_o.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=pa-GOVt4JtMAX-A7GmK&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=30&amp;oh=d31f5ee8212a8fe3516bd0f343819609&amp;oe=603B1A1B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp526x296%2F142880139_1928896283932955_5605947646482050194_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3Dpa-GOVt4JtMAX-A7GmK%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D30%26oh%3Dd31f5ee8212a8fe3516bd0f343819609%26oe%3D603B1A1B&h=4fcf4e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIn Elon papa we trust! SH!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4068e15e24fdb3cd85ef2f2080c5c9935bb4832","tid":2386196,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}